     fhir:div "<div xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"><p>This value set includes codes based on the following rules:</p><ul><li>Include these codes as defined in <a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-allergy-intolerance-category.html\"><code>http://hl7.org/fhir/allergy-intolerance-category</code></a><table class=\"none\"><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\"><b>Code</b></td><td><b>Display</b></td><td><b>Definition</b></td><td><b><a href=\"ConceptMap-CMVFallergySubstanceCategory.html\">VF_allergySubstanceCategory</a></b></td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-allergy-intolerance-category.html#allergy-intolerance-category-medication\">medication</a></td><td>medication</td><td>Substances administered to achieve a physiological effect.</td><td/></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-allergy-intolerance-category.html#allergy-intolerance-category-food\">food</a></td><td style=\"color: #cccccc\">Food</td><td>Any substance consumed to provide nutritional support for the body.</td><td/></tr></table></li><li>Include these codes as defined in <code>http://va.gov/terminology/vistaDefinedTerms/120.8-3.1</code><table class=\"none\"><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\"><b>Code</b></td><td><b>Display</b></td><td><b><a href=\"ConceptMap-CMVFallergySubstanceCategory.html\">VF_allergySubstanceCategory</a></b></td></tr><tr><td>D</td><td>DRUG</td><td><span title=\"EQUIVALENT\">~</span><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-allergy-intolerance-category.html#allergy-intolerance-category-medication\">medication</a></td></tr><tr><td>F</td><td>FOOD</td><td><span title=\"EQUIVALENT\">~</span><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-allergy-intolerance-category.html#allergy-intolerance-category-food\">food</a></td></tr><tr><td>O</td><td>OTHER</td><td/></tr></table></li></ul></div>"
